sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Flutter App
    participant SQLite as Local SQLite
    participant PG as PostgreSQL

    Note over App,PG: Push Phase

    App->>SQLite: Query rows where synced_at IS NULL OR updated_at > synced_at
    SQLite-->>App: Changed rows

    App->>App: Partition changed rows into batches of 50

    loop For each batch of up to 50 rows
        loop For each row in batch — conflict detection
            App->>PG: Fetch current remote version of row
            PG-->>App: Remote row (or not found)

            alt local.updated_at > remote.updated_at
                Note over App: Local wins — field-by-field merge
            else remote.updated_at within conflict threshold
                Note over App: Flag for user review
            else remote.updated_at >= local.updated_at
                Note over App: Remote wins for conflicting fields
            end
        end

        App->>PG: Multi-row INSERT...ON CONFLICT DO UPDATE (batch)
        PG-->>App: OK
        App->>SQLite: Update synced_at = now() for all rows in batch
        App->>SQLite: Write to sync_log (direction=push, batch_size=N)
    end

    Note over App,PG: Pull Phase

    App->>PG: Query rows where updated_at > last_synced_at (per table)
    PG-->>App: Remote changes

    loop For each remote row
        App->>SQLite: Fetch local version of row
        SQLite-->>App: Local row (or not found)

        alt Row not found locally
            App->>SQLite: Insert new row
        else local.updated_at > remote.updated_at
            Note over App: Local wins — skip remote value
        else
            App->>SQLite: Merge remote values into local row
        end

        App->>SQLite: Write to sync_log (direction=pull)
    end

    Note over App,SQLite: Sync complete
